  "implementation_guidance": {
    "recommended_approach": "Phase 1: Stand up Redis alongside existing PostgreSQL. Implement Location Ingestion Service writing to both (Redis with TTL, PostgreSQL async). Implement LocationReadService that reads exclusively from Redis. Phase 2: Add Push Gateway with SSE (simpler than WebSocket initially). Phase 3: Add WebSocket support and Staleness Enforcement Middleware for defense-in-depth. Each phase is independently deployable and valuable.",
